libterm-table-perl (0.015-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add libunicode-linebreak-perl to Build-Depends-Indep and Recommends.
    Thanks to Jonas Smedegaard for the bug report. (Closes: #948245)
  * Drop alternative build dependency for Test::More.
  * Update years of packaging copyright.
  * Annotate test-only build dependencies with <!nocheck>.
  * Set upstream metadata fields: Bug-Submit, Repository, Repository-
    Browse.

